<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= full_title(yield(:title)) %></title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%= yield(:title) %></h1>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">What Does PDRank Do?</h2>
        <p class="lead">PDRank is a multi-platform app that helps healthcare providers query details
          about the latest treatments for patients with a certain set of conditions, no longer requiring
          experienced doctors to continuously read papers to stay up to date.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/assets/PDRankLogo" id="featuretteimages">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">What do we do? <span class="text-muted">Help you find the documents you need.</span></h2>
        <p class="lead">Provide a platform where healthcare professionals can quickly search for up-to-date treatment options from our database of scientific journals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/assets/icon-what-we-do.png" id="featuretteimages">
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette">
      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="featurette-heading">Who are we? <span class="text-muted"></span></h2>
        <p class="lead">We are PDRank, a group of developers that strive to find the latest and most effective treatments for patients using clustering and various language processing techinques.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-5">
        <img src="/assets/whoarewe.png" id="featuretteimages">
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">


